    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "• Expert Analysis Framework. We prompt the LLM to consider how different MCTs may be related to the remediation of vulnerabilities (e.g., line additions might indicate the introduction of new security checks). The model is guided to integrate multi-source data with its reasoning capabilities in order to identify the methods most associated with vulnerability and explain the rationale behind its conclusions.",
